result.name: Koon Thai Cuisine

reviews.text: I am no food critic but certainly am a big fan of Thai food.  Was suggested this place for lunch, turned out not to be as satisfying as I have thought.  I hesitated to say they serve authentic Thai food, or it was some kind of Thai food that I have never tasted before, looked no different though.  Did not taste right, not to mention good.  You may want to try it if you love to challenge strangely flavored exotic food.  It was the decent environment and service that earned the second star.
Wouldnt say things taste authentic thai, but the food is great nonetheless, and the yellow curry here is amazing!
Food are too salty for me
Really good food and atmosphere. We loved the mango beef stir fry.

This is a decent Thai restaurant with good offerings of Thai dishes. We ordered the pork with chilli and basil. Good but I would have preferred it to be spicier and less “wet”. The Thai style morning glory is ok but the red curry chicken a bit bland. 
Service was ok but slightly lacking in attention to details.

reviews.text: I am no food critic but certainly am a big fan of Thai food.  Was suggested this place for lunch, turned out not to be as satisfying as I have thought.  I hesitated to say they serve authentic Thai food, or it was some kind of Thai food that I have never tasted before, looked no different though.  Did not taste right, not to mention good.  You may want to try it if you love to challenge strangely flavored exotic food.  It was the decent environment and service that earned the second star.
好味道，特別是青咖哩，百香果蜜就麻麻

差評！同行者全都腸胃炎！海南雞嫌疑最大！
同朋友行開油麻地，見到有間樓上泰國菜，咪試下新野
一入去，幾丁友，深感不妙，個侍應仲問有冇book.......乜需要咩？！早知當時就走人
坐低叫了三樣：半隻海南雞、金邊粉、小食併盆，加一人一隻椰青；三樣野食好普通，椰青反而唔錯，埋單500蚊落樓，餐飯叫做不過不失.......
但跟住先蒞料！
個晚個肚已經隱隱痛，半夜典床典席，到頂唔順衝入廁所已經係朝早，到呢刻痾咗5-6次，就脫水，再係咁我就要睇醫生；問friend 點（註：食雞食了大半），原來已去睇醫生，確診腸胃炎，打了針要sick leave 在家休息
我地唔會告你，但要打上蒞告誡各位想做勇士嘅人：千祈唔好食呢間野！除非想第日射波！
Openrice 打手，扣起我篇留言，所以係度提醒大家！！😡
味道不錯，服務好，座位寬敞舒適😀
